{
  "text": "We fail to reproduce the results reported in [CITATION_1] by using the provided settings, which is also observed in the ResNet-101 in Section 6.5. Each block, B01, B02, . . . , is a 3-layer bottleneck block [CITATION_2] . The dashed line indicates the projection shortcut with a 1 \u00d7 1 convolutional layer. The pooling layers are omitted for simplicity.",
